We have installed stepping stones as a substitute for the
collapsed bridge. Please use them as a temporary measure until
the repair budget is approved. You can jump towards the stepping
stones by pressing the confirm button.

The text is barely readable, it's blurry... It seems like the
bridge won't be repaired.
\SE[51] (...It's frustrating, but it was a little fun.)

\SE[7]It seems like you really liked it, huh? \.You can come play
again if you want.

\SE[102]I-I'm not enjoying it, okay!? \!\SE[51]Besides, while I'm
here like this, Lunaroa is still captured....

\SE[2]...Still captured? \SE[3]What? Do you also have someone you
know who's been captured?

\SE[2]Ah, yeah.... \!Is it because we're wearing the same
uniform?\. When I entered the country, someone I knew got
captured....

\SE[7]Then let's hurry up and move forward. \.It's good to save
time.
